data.description: This single-owner custom colonial is perched high on a bluff at the end of a cul-de-sac, offering unobstructed panoramic views of Cape Cod Bay from the Canal to Provincetown. The new owners will enjoy this flexible 4000+ sq ft open floor plan that encompasses three above-ground levels of living and features a gourmet kitchen, hardwood flooring, first and second-floor living room areas, and a carefully maintained interior and exterior. Spoil yourself with a 900+ sq ft primary suite with a walk-in closet, study/dressing room, and a luxurious bathroom - all designed to take in the views. Easily access miles of unspoiled beaches and undeveloped acreage of Ellisville State Park using a nearby path located within the neighborhood. Rather than fighting bridge traffic and construction, enjoy the convenience of being less than 1 mile from route 3 and arrive early to your oasis and immerse yourself in the best that coastal living has to offer.
